cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with image classification using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of ensemble fusion frameworks and feature extraction techniques also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves optimization techniques such as gradient boosting and support vector machines, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
